" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.musicweb-international.com/classRev/2003/Apr03/british_choral_music.htm\">\"Review: British Choral Music\"</a>. MusicWeb International.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Review%3A+British+Choral+Music&amp;rft.pub=MusicWeb+International&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.aulast=Culot&amp;rft.aufirst=Hubert&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.musicweb-international.com%2FclassRev%2F2003%2FApr03%2Fbritish_choral_music.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AA+Colour+Symphony\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.simonlindley.org.uk/howells.html\">Romanticism in Retrospect</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.emusic.com/lists/showlist.html?lid=16782048\">The eMusic Dozen: British Composers</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-greene-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-greene_8-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=m3S7PIxe0mwC&amp;pg=PA1199&amp;lpg=PA1199&amp;dq=bliss+colour+symphony+gloucester&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=KT7QuTP2Va&amp;sig=7HENnXAqSA-G0UcegzQHMFAQ0Oc&amp;hl=en&amp;ei=VZ3RSb_iL6Xg6gPx_6yaBA&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;resnum=3&amp;ct=result\">Greene's Biographical Encyclopedia of Composers</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ans